[There is no reference to the outbreak reported here for 28 Oct 2018 but it might have been a late case following on from the previous
outbreaks in that month. They have ignored the 2020 incident when the human may have been exposed to a dead bovine. They list all the other animals in this zoo so theoretically there could have been ample opportunity for other animals to have been exposed by the source, not just the other 7 horses. A puzzle. - Mod.MHJ

